snippet.title: CYGNI: All Guns Blazing Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Get your flight suit ready and double-time it to the flight deck, your ORCA fighter is ready for take off!

CYGNI: All Guns Blazing launches August 6! Give'em hell!

Pre-order now on Steam® and Playstation®5: 
· STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1248080/CYGNI_All_Guns_Blazing/ 
· PS5: https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10004231/ 

Keep an eye on our dedicated channels for further information and updates: 
· X - https://x.com/CygniGame
· Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/Cygnigame
· Official Website - https://www.cygnigame.com/
· TikTok - https://www.tiktok.com/@cygnigame?lang=en

#CygniGame #Keelworks #Konami
